Trade/Device Name(s): GoodLife CS-200 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
GoodLife CS-200 Professional Blood Glucose Monitoring System
GoodLife KP Blood Glucose Test Strips
GoodLife KP Professional Blood Glucose Test Strip
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): GoodLife CS-200 Professional Blood Glucose Meter
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for GoodLife CS-200 Blood Glucose Monitoring System and CS-200 Professional Blood Glucose Monitoring System for quantitative glucose measurement using amperometric electrochemical biosensor technology.
Indications for Use Summary: For quantitative measurement of glucose in whole blood (capillary for single patient use; capillary, venous, or arterial for professional use) to aid in monitoring effectiveness of diabetes control, not for diagnosis or screening of diabetes or neonatal use.
